{"legislative_session": "20252026", "identifier": "AB2375", "title": "Alcoholic beverages: beer.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["bill"], "subject": ["Alcoholicbeverages", "beer"], "abstracts": [{"note": "summary", "abstract": "Existing law defines \"beer\" for purposes of the Alcoholic Beverage Control Act as any alcoholic beverage obtained by the fermentation of any infusion or decoction of barley, malt, hops, or any other similar product, or any combination thereof in water, as specified.\n\nThis bill would revise the definition of \"beer\" for purposes of the act to provide that beer may be produced using other grain and to specify that fermentation occurs in drinkable water."}], "other_titles": [], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-ca-20252026-ab2375"}], "actions": [{"description": "Read first time. To print.", "date": "2026-02-19", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["reading-1"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "From printer. May be heard in committee March 22.", "date": "2026-02-20", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Referred to Com. on G.O.", "date": "2026-03-09", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on G.O.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "From committee: Do pass. To Consent Calendar. (Ayes 22. Noes 0.) (April 8).", "date": "2026-04-09", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["committee-passage", "committee-passage-favorable"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Read second time. Ordered to Consent Calendar.", "date": "2026-04-13", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["reading-1", "reading-2"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Read third time. 